\hypertarget{aerovision-uav-flight-software-engineer-technical-challenge}{%
\section{AeroVision UAV --- Flight Software Engineer Technical Challenge}\label{aerovision-uav-flight-software-engineer-technical-challenge}}

Attitude Estimation and Control from Raw IMU Data

Position: Flight Software Engineer • Team: Autopilot Development\\
Pre-Interview Technical Assessment • Estimated Time: 3 Hours

\hypertarget{company-brief-aerovision-uav}{%
\subsection{Company Brief: AeroVision UAV}\label{company-brief-aerovision-uav}}

\textbf{Scenario:} AeroVision UAV builds autonomous quadrotor platforms for aerial inspection and mapping. Your team has collected 10 seconds of high-rate sensor data from a test flight including raw IMU readings, desired attitude commands, motor telemetry, and ground truth pose. As part of this challenge, you will implement attitude estimation and control pipelines as ROS2 nodes.

